<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Registered Residential Carpenter (RRC) | Carpenters for Housing Reform Victoria</title>
  <meta name="description" content="A practical, builder-supportive reform proposal for a Registered Residential Carpenter pathway in Victoria." />
  <style>
    body { margin:0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background:#07110b; color:#fff; }
    .container { max-width:1100px; margin:auto; padding:20px; }
    h1, h2, h3 { color:#2d9b61; }
    .btn { display:inline-block; padding:12px 20px; margin:10px 10px 10px 0; background:#1c784a; color:#fff; text-decoration:none; border-radius:6px; }
    .section { margin-bottom:40px; }
    .box { background:#0f1b14; padding:20px; border-radius:10px; margin-bottom:15px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

  <h1>Registered Residential Carpenter (RRC)</h1>
  <p>A practical reform to improve renovation delivery in Victoria.</p>

  <a class="btn" href="RRC_Policy_Brief_Victoria_Final.pdf" target="_blank">Download Policy Brief</a>
  <a class="btn" href="RRC_Executive_Summary_Victoria.pdf" target="_blank">Download Executive Summary</a>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>The Problem</h2>
    <div class="box">Small renovation projects are delayed due to builder availability.</div>
    <div class="box">Builders are overloaded with projects that could be better allocated.</div>
    <div class="box">Experienced carpenters are underutilised.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>The Solution</h2>
    <div class="box">Introduce a Registered Residential Carpenter (RRC) pathway.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <div class="box">Tier 1: 10+ years experience, up to $100k projects</div>
    <div class="box">Tier 2: 20+ years experience, up to $200k projects</div>
    <div class="box">Oversight required above $75k</div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Safeguards</h2>
    <div class="box">Strict exclusions on new builds and complex structural work</div>
    <div class="box">Mandatory insurance on all projects</div>
    <div class="box">Compliance and audit enforcement</div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Contact / Feedback</h2>
    <iframe src="YOUR_GOOGLE_FORM_EMBED_URL_HERE" style="width:100%; height:400px; border:none;"></iframe>
  </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
